beer.beer_description: If you like an espresso martini you're going to love this as soon as you open the can. You'll be warmly greeted with a Bold Coffee knows roasting vanilla caramel butter Rome and raising. Your first sip let you know this is different from other coffee beers it's a logger with a smooth profile and clean finished that's perfectly integrated with single origin cold brew coffee. Knock it back with your Christmas pudding
